Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.70,0:01:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咕呵~早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.10,0:01:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咕呵~起床吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.59,0:01:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咕呵~小要 遲到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.09,0:01:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咕呵~早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.19,0:01:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咕呵~起床吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.99,0:02:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…痛死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.89,0:02:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Merida島
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來請看這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是相良中士曾參加過的一次戰鬥的畫面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前曾跟我們交過手的AS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.01,0:02:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代號確定為「猛毒」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別值得注意的是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.31,0:02:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與發光現象同時發生的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.31,0:02:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有著某種力量能把所有攻擊無效化
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.61,0:02:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這表明它搭載著λ-Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該和相良中士的Arbalest上的裝置 幾乎完全相同
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.91,0:02:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.91,0:02:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼? 威巴中士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,λ-Driver是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於那個就由上校閣下來解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.02,0:03:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.22,0:03:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於這屬於機密事項
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從來沒能向大家解釋清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.52,0:03:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在這裡解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,λ-Driver也就是虛擬斥力場發生裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說白了就是把駕駛員的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.32,0:03:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接轉變成物理性的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說把子彈反彈 破壞目標等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為我在開玩笑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提問
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說吧 瑪奧上士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.71,0:03:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼萬能的話 為什麼宗介不常用它呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.01,0:03:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一次也沒看到他用過這種力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實 那是因為這個裝置的效果很不穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.01,0:04:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如剛才所說 要能把人類的意識反映出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要很大的集中力才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.90,0:04:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中力?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.49,0:04:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說要在生死關頭的極限時刻才能發動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.09,0:04:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒達到那個水平的話就不能發動了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.79,0:04:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺以前和我戰鬥過的敵人可以隨意使用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.29,0:04:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們怎麼做到的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不能斷言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.59,0:04:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要麼是進行了相當程度的嚴格訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是使用了某種藥物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人為強制進入那種狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.89,0:04:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提問…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 楊伍長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.29,0:04:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除Arbalest以外 還有搭載著λ-Driver的機體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mithril內部也進行著新裝置的研究和開發
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但由於各種各樣的原因 目前我們毫無收穫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:05:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說只有相良中士才能和他戰鬥?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不一定絕對是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如沒有λ-Driver而進行交戰的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.69,0:05:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必需有死傷慘重的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要竊竊私語
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,λ-Driver的應對方案目前正在研究中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.19,0:05:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦有報告出來 就會告訴你們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.69,0:05:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解散
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良中士傳來關於雷斯的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.09,0:05:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 我會過目的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.79,0:05:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護任務啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不知道誰在盯著小要的現在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.20,0:05:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把身為wisper的她交給相良和雷斯兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.20,0:05:46.80,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}wisper: 耳語者,傾聽者的大腦裡先天擁有黑科技的資料，表面和普通人無異\N但是在精神領域和常人有非常大的差異，並且傾聽者之間可以發生共振
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是太鬆懈了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們的人員也是有限的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,0:06:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但又不能把耳語者擁有的黑暗科技知識交出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.51,0:06:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耳語者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.41,0:06:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 小要也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是聽不到那種聲音的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.71,0:06:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否以一個普通女孩的身份生活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.01,0:06:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 小要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.59,0:06:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.99,0:06:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了一個很有意思的網站
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.18,0:06:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.38,0:06:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.88,0:06:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考試的資料都…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的3天來的勞動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屋頂上有什麼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.10,0:06:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咯 小要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.29,0:07:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鳥啊 看看這個雷達
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就連防空都…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把它停掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然打人 會很痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.29,0:07:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 連一點長進都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦算了 相良君也正在反省
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.49,0:07:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.59,0:07:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事 風間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在和你說不太方便
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一個論壇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從昨天的晚上開始就這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道是怎麼拍的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.69,0:07:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在向敵人暴露身份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是快點找到犯人並阻止他 相良君?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.29,0:07:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 別介意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 風間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好還是別讓本人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.60,0:07:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她會受傷害的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.12,0:07:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般來說吧 所以最好還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦 剛才開始兩個人就鬼鬼祟祟的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.42,0:07:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.32,0:08:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你盡興地享受往日般的校園生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常的不自然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.53,0:08:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 老師的情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微穩定一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.53,0:08:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藥開始起作用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,備用的繃帶快完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等會要去買了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.32,0:08:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.82,0:08:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去給老師擦身體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:09:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 能撐到什麼時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.72,0:09:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.22,0:09:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.72,0:09:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 我們又見到老師了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.92,0:09:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍著點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.80,0:09:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.10,0:09:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:10:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鳥同學 這是你上次說想聽的CD
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹嗎 宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.70,0:10:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.10,0:10:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 千鳥 關於上次的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別出聲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.90,0:10:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.50,0:10:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你一定是要跟來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.80,0:10:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢話啊 為什麼我會悲哀到要你在女廁外面等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.60,0:10:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼至少在你進去之前和出來後\N讓我仔細檢查一下廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這變態
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小要 冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.30,0:10:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色鬼色鬼色鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的相良有點怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此纏著人 真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.41,0:10:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是還是有點像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.81,0:10:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:11:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗介的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像剛來學校的時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是在幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.11,0:11:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說「怎麼了」你到底在這裡幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.01,0:11:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調查
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.61,0:11:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查什麼啊 現在就給我停下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.01,0:11:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你幹嗎 給我停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.51,0:11:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別弄壞它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.51,0:11:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 我的電腦…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.91,0:11:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了 為什麼總是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.41,0:11:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是他們留下來的裝備啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 是Mithril啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:11:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能就那麼肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:11:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向南飛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個腳印是M9型號吧 應該是3架
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.98,0:12:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不能確定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.28,0:12:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空降後摧毀高威脅的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.47,0:12:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮壓防空設施 然後再移動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的集合點有變化
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一台機體從部隊裡分離出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.37,0:12:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去處是 應該是防空陣地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡還無法確認
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以把坦克的主炮攻擊反彈掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.97,0:12:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了λ-Driver外 沒其他的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.97,0:12:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能只從那個就斷定…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.68,0:12:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個白色AS
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顏色的話可以隨意變換
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.48,0:12:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 那個白色的AS突破了巴黎克軍的防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃啊逃啊逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.98,0:12:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦等等 敵人的追兵要跟上來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 我解說的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.31,0:12:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇哇 把武器扔下了 沒子彈了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.91,0:13:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了橋中間又被兩岸包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 危機
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這時他向水裡跳下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.11,0:13:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 戰鬥記錄也就如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 該見見客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.11,0:13:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後永遠也不要發生這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.99,0:13:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.29,0:13:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.99,0:13:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊 宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.69,0:13:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼說也很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.69,0:13:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 沒什麼 你多心了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…不想說的話就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.89,0:13:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.69,0:13:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想付錢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.28,0:14:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 你們所說的高性能武器屁用都沒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會付錢的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.08,0:14:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我滾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你媽媽沒教你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.48,0:14:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果遇到可怕的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.48,0:14:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看好錢包和屁眼麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.28,0:14:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.78,0:14:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵 沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.00,0:14:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我胡扯的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A ve maria~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:15:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.32,0:15:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是偷拍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我建議宗介在不告知千鳥的狀態下抓犯人的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我不忍看下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹這個的人應該天誅 天誅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.42,0:15:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實犯人還沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒找到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.72,0:15:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 有眉目了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.62,0:15:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.72,0:15:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷拍用的裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換衣室的天花板上找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪 那個檢查是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了找這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經調查過它的頻率了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來進行逆向跟蹤就可以找到犯人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 宗介了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.61,0:15:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.11,0:15:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.51,0:15:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.31,0:15:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方向090 距離5米
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.01,0:15:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是隔壁的教室
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.09,0:15:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔下武器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.79,0:15:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,張開手腳趴在地上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆子啊 考慮常識啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這是在室內的突擊最有效..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.99,0:16:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你也不能在學校牆上開一個洞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.29,0:16:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.29,0:16:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要追了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A ve maria
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話欠款豈不是拿不回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你命令的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別亂說話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.30,0:16:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽應該總是會教導你不能推卸責任給別人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.20,0:16:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 啊 聽見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.80,0:16:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 死了 又死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.70,0:16:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 這個世界到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.50,0:16:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會充滿了殘酷的死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:17:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好悲哀 非常悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡似的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.20,0:17:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.10,0:17:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.60,0:17:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先看看這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再接近的話就把這個丟臉的照片發到全世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是十惡不赦 不合常理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 你有資格說別人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.91,0:17:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了麼 知道的話就給我快點滾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.91,0:17:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為男人 真夠差勁的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.31,0:17:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了麼 這是報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.61,0:17:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報仇?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 學生會選拔輸給你的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.01,0:17:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用我詳細解釋了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.21,0:17:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰來的?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.31,0:17:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.51,0:17:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把這個發到全世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀了你的聲譽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.01,0:17:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好嘗嘗我的怨恨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.41,0:17:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是普通的報復呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.11,0:17:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別做傻事了 冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…叫你別過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.19,0:18:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要按了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.99,0:18:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 射殺他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉他 不 別別
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按…要按了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不讓那個圖像發出去就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.29,0:18:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那事情就好辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.99,0:18:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.78,0:18:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.78,0:18:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.48,0:18:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 說那些話的是這個嘴巴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.88,0:18:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊? 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.88,0:18:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打屁股了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.88,0:19:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘖 無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退了 給我快點收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.08,0:19:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的老師餵魚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.99,0:19:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,節哀順變
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.61,0:19:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呦 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會主動打來 真是少有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.61,0:19:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.81,0:19:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你撿到老師了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.01,0:19:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消息很靈通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.61,0:20:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的話 我希望你們能老實點的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.21,0:20:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是忠告嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.61,0:20:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,況且是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安心吧 沒打算惹麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以相信你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.41,0:20:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.78,0:20:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請…請放過我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就說實話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找千鳥的麻煩真正目的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.08,0:20:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛說實話啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想和我裝傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就拷問你的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先是一根指頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.37,0:20:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪一根
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.27,0:20:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 別幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.87,0:20:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了 對方可是普通的高中生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.77,0:20:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了 今天早上偷窺我公寓的也是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.97,0:20:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不知道 我只在校內幹過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.18,0:20:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.78,0:20:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.68,0:20:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺了不起的演技啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.78,0:20:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是對我來說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.88,0:20:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.58,0:21:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.08,0:21:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.58,0:21:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 還沒有審問
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 今天早上的到底是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個雷達好大的威力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又得買新手機了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 想拉大便
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.15,0:22:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}きっと君は今日の日も
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.15,0:22:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}你今天一定也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.20,0:22:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}真っ直ぐ明日を見てる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.20,0:22:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}直視著明天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.21,0:22:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}風が吹くあの丘に咲いた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.21,0:22:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}彷彿在那微風吹過的山丘上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.92,0:22:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}向日葵のように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.92,0:22:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}綻放的向日葵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.46,0:22:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}どんなに遠く離れていても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.46,0:22:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}即使相離再遙遠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.52,0:22:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}この歌声が君に届くように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.52,0:22:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}也要把這歌聲傳遞給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.47,0:22:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}涙がずっと止まらない夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.47,0:22:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}在這滿臉淚痕的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}君の窓を照らす月になりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}希望成為照亮你窗前的月光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:23:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}また必ず会えると そう思うから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:23:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}一定會再相見的 我這麼相信著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.08,0:23:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似曾相識的敵人的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.91,0:23:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔絕於地底的戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.01,0:23:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有將要見面的機體之迷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.81,0:23:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 那也並不是一場艱難的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.11,0:23:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷宮和龍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.70,0:23:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深淵中的蜘蛛絲正向我們的手足襲來
